    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>egg[s]</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>half </strong>your <strong>white wine vinegar </strong>(you'll use the rest later!)</p><p>Tip: This will prevent the egg from cracking!</p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat and once boiling, cook for exactly 8 min for the perfect, mid-boiled egg</p><p>Fill a bowl of <strong>very cold water</strong> and add the <strong>cooked egg[s] </strong>to the bowl and set aside for later</p>",
