      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drain the <strong>pomegranate seeds</strong> in a fine sieve and set <strong>half</strong> of them aside for later</p><p>Place the sieve with the <strong>remaining pomegranate seeds </strong>over a bowl</p><p>Crush the seeds with a fork to release the <strong>pomegranate juice</strong></p><p>Tip: Lay a piece of cling film over the sieve to prevent mess!</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
