    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and grate your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>tomato[es]</strong> finely</p><p>Wash your<strong> lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper and shred it finely</p><p>Peel the <strong>cooled egg[s]</strong> and cut into quarters</p>",
