    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>pomegranate juice </strong>and<strong> tahini</strong> in a bowl with your <strong>mayo </strong>and<strong> grated garlic </strong>(not a big garlic fan? Try using less!)</p><p>Add<strong> half</strong> your <strong>honey</strong> (you'll use the rest later!) and the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>white wine vinegar </strong>and give it a good mix up – this is your <strong>tahini & pomegranate ranch dressing</strong></p>",
