    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the potatoes are golden and crisp, remove the tray[s] from the oven, crumble your <strong>feta</strong> over and drizzle with the <strong>remaining honey</strong></p><p>Return the tray[s] to the oven for a final 5 min or until the feta is slightly melted and golden – these are your <strong>feta & honey roast potatoes</strong></p>",
